name: .DISCORDBOT File Extension
summary: Learn about .DISCORDBOT files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: To open a DISCORDBOT file in Discord Bot Maker, click the File button located in the program's menu bar. Then, select Open Existing Project, navigate to your bot's main directory, and open your project.discordbot file.
